_sText:
I decided to work with hammer, before 1 month.
So this is my first product.
I hope you enjoy.
It is a surf map with 3 Stages , 1 Bonusstage and a jail.
You have 3 minutes to beat the map, before all players are teleported in the jail.
If you are in lvl 3, you have a better position in jail, than someone who ist in lvl1.
But i think you know the concept.
Nothing special but i think it turned out well.
